{"tid":442624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[看破紅塵]有無人已經睇化一切?","createTime":"2017-10-20T21:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T05:13:02.000Z","uid":153493,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4c0e15c1a9fe54aae81546e4bca4d91ed7d316","tid":442624,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T21:19:53.000Z","msg":"看破紅塵同睇化一切<br />\n並唔撚係話睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得要重刷輕生投胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而係當自己嘅人生閱歷多左<br />\neg見識過唔少賤人仆街壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者自己做過傻仔又好<br />\n唔夠聰明唔夠競爭力優點唔多都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人變得睇化睇開好多<br />\n唔會再好似以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多人同事都執著落去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌一撚早看破紅塵啦屌,只係繼續人生旅途<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野看破紅塵呀,<br />\n活著很累"},{"pid":"3b4043cbe5eb450982a5d13b8a13226bf825a2bb","tid":442624,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T21:37:31.000Z","msg":"咁樣只係睇清楚呢個世界同埋人性，之後不願面對<br />\n真係睇化你根本唔會理個世界係點<br />\n因為你已經接受左佢係咁<br />\n同埋知道自己改變唔到佢<br />\n利伸：未睇化"},{"pid":"9c0198820becaf67e0384b5ded018088715c92ff","tid